Author: fishonthesun
Text: My grandpa came over to show me how he makes bread. He was just eyeballing the recipe, measuring things into his hand for tablespoons. One of the things called for 1 cup n he was like "I'm just gonna use the rest of the bag" which was easily 2 cups. The bread came out fine but I cant eat it cause I had no control over it and dont know the true calories
